show.title: At 30, I Have a Lot of Pocket Money
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने Kuku FM (Android)  पर यह शो सुना और मुझे यकीन है कि आपको भी यह जरूर पसंद आएगा। 
https://links.kukufm.com/Y8tgCV
show.description: Just as he steps into his thirties, a man with endless pocket money dives into the city’s chaos, chasing opportunity and ambition. From street stalls to business empires, his rise is marked by misunderstandings, betrayals—and moments that force him to confront his true self. At 30, I Have a Lot of Pocket Money  is an urban short drama about wealth, transformation, and the price of growth.
